A simple mesh libarary
=====================================

-------------------------------------
[Name]
MeshLib Libraray

-------------------------------------
[Developer]
Xu Dong : before 2006
hywei   : 2010 -- 

------------------------------------
[Goal]
A general, flexible, efficient and easy-to-use mesh libraray for research purpose.
Supporting arbitray polygonal meshes as input, but with a primary focus on triangle
meshes now.

